name: Mille Premi con il Concorso di Shirab

description: Bruce Wayne will use any method to solve a crime--especially the disappearance that's been plaguing him for twenty years. But will allowing a local reporter to shadow him for a day get the results he wants? "Reporter's Notebook" part 1 of 1.
name: Reporter's Notebook, Part 1 of 1

description: This is where it all began. Before he was Master Chief, he was John - a boy stolen from his parents and conscripted into the SPARTAN II program on the fortress world of Reach. These are desperate times in the human colonies, with galactic civil war just a heartbeat away, and only Dr. Catherine Halsey understands the terrible price humanity must pay to keep from destroying itself. Brian Reed (AMAZING SPIDER-MAN PRESENTS: AMERICAN SON), and Felix Ruiz (MARVEL BOY: THE URANIAN) bring you an adaptation of the best-selling novel HALO: FALL OF REACH by Eric Nylund. Collecting HALO: FALL OF REACH - BOOT CAMP #1-4.
name: HC

volume.name: Halo: Fall of Reach - Boot Camp

name: In Regalo la Prima "Cartina Poster" dell'Atlante

description: Who buys Zac-stuff is 'in'. Thus Fanny is mainly interested in Zac-clothing and Kiekeboe in Zac-shares. There is much fake Zac-articles on the market. Meanwhile Konstantinopel gets kidnapped and taken to Istanbul. Charlotte and Marcel try to find him there. That trail leads them to the fakers of the Zac-articles.
name: Konstantinopel In Istanboel

description: Kiekeboe has an original gift for Charlotte for their 20th anniversary: a pie with a valuable ring in it. It takes several suprising adventures before he can present the pie to Charlotte.
name: De Taart

description: Kiekeboe wakes up in a cinema room and he doesn't remember what has happened in the last few days. The reconstruction of his memory leads to a plastic surgeon with a preference for American comic characters and a mysterious, famous man who wants to change his face.
name: Black-out

description: Again Bibi Pralin Gaga has new powermad plans. Via the Medusa-foundation he wants to spread out genetically identical Gaga-babies over the world. His headquarters is a yacht at the Côte d'Allure. All seems to go wel until Fanny shows up.
name: De Medusa-Stichting

description: Kiekeboe is having a party because he's about to have his 50th adventure. But there's no time for partying, because Kiekeboe learns he has just three days to live. He wanders around dazed while Fanny looks into strips rejected by Merho.
name: Afgelast Wegens Ziekte

volume.name: Families of Altered Wars Presents Angels 750
Foul Play: The Art and Artists of the Notorious 1950s E.C. Comics!

deck: The first issue of Dennis & Gnasher Megazine, but despite proclaiming that it's issue No. 1, the small print next to the barcode calls it BeanoMAX #80.
name: Dennis & Gnasher Megazine Issue No. 1

description: Piyoko and her Dark Gema Gema Gang have blown into town but their evil plans are quickly going awry. They've been outwitted by Digiko and they're slowly starving to death. Everyone knows crime doesn't pay. Now it's time for Piyoko and her crew to look for real jobs!
name: Vol. 3
Are We Out of the Driveway Yet?

description: The demon Adramelech has returned to play another "game" with Doctor Xander Crowe, and this time he has possessed the daughter of Los Angeles mob boss Don Marino! Caught between Hell and the mob, Crowe is forced to rely on Sparrow to find a special artifact known as the Ring of Solomon. But can Sparrow find the ring before Amanda Marino escapes her bonds and wreaks havoc at the Marino estate?

This four-story anthology brings together a wide variety of artists to create different visions of Sparrow and Doctor Xander Crowe, while still retaining the visual look created by lead series artist Jared Souza. The tales in this volume range from comedic to gothic ghost story to melancholy noir -- a perfect Halloween sampler for fans and newcomers alike!

description: Don’t miss your chance to discover the superstar characters and creators of tomorrow!

What if being a super hero was just like any other job? What if you fell in love with your arch enemy? What if your sidekick had a crush on you? Meet Jacob Reilly, aka Flame-O. He didn't want to be a hero, he wanted to be a rock star, but now he's stuck working for Heroes for Zeroes, and his life is about to get, really, really complicated.
